      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected and preserved to the highest standards, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
