    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty\u2014it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. There isn't a single scratch or dent to be found, and it still has that wonderful new car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is a museum-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 (FD), a pinnacle of 90s Japanese engineering. This specimen retains its original 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The chassis architecture features a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring surgical precision and 50:50 weight distribution. Every vacuum line has been meticulously inspected, and the cooling system remains within factory thermal parameters. The exterior showcases flawless Montego Blue Mica paint with no clear coat failure, while the interior is a time-capsule of unblemished upholstery and fully functional analog instrumentation. A rare, mechanically pristine example for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising performance and originality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless paint. Pristine interior. Full service records included. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, while the factory wheels remain unblemished. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery retains its original texture and scent, with zero signs of bolster wear or carpet fading. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records. It has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in rain, and meticulously detailed after every outing. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example that provides a genuine new-car driving experience.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
